{"type":"message","id":"15a7709b","parentId":"c034a804","timestamp":"2026-03-14T14:30:27.607Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The skill seems incomplete or has issues. Let me try a different approach - maybe use the web to search for logo design services or use a browser to access a free logo generator.\n\nActually, let me try using the browser to create a logo design concept or find alternatives. Or I can suggest using a free online logo maker.\n\nActually, I should let the user know about the issue and suggest alternatives:\n1. Use an online logo maker (like canva, logomaker.ai, etc.)\n2. Use Figma for design\n3. Hire a designer on platforms like 99designs, fiverr\n\nLet me inform Roger about this and provide alternatives.","thinkingSignature":"0d419fe064d9fb2d37e0b38a0daa5f89ca3afb715c868846258d39c3c774e9e1"},{"type":"text","text":"图片生成技能暂时不可用（依赖包问题）。我建议用以下方式获取Logo：\n\n---\n\n## 🎨 Logo设计方案\n\n### 方案1：在线生成（免费/付费）\n| 工具 | 网址 | 费用 |\n|------|------|------|\n| Canva | canva.com | 免费版够用 |\n| LogoAI | logoai.com | ¥29起 |\n| 标智客 | biaomake.com | 免费 |\n\n### 方案2：AI生成\n| 工具 | 网址 | 费用 |\n|------|------|------|\n| Midjourney | midjourney.com | $10/月 |\n| Leonardo.ai | leonardo.ai | 免费 |\n\n### 方案3：外包设计\n| 平台 | 网址 | 费用 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 猪八戒 | zbj.com | ¥200起 |\n| Fiverr | fiverr.com | $5起 |\n\n---\n\n## 💡 MNEX Logo设计建议\n\n**风格**：科技感 + 专业感\n\n**元素建议**：\n- 字母\"M\"为主形（MNEX首字母）\n- 加入\"网络节点\"或\"专利文件\"元素\n- 配色：蓝紫渐变（科技感）\n\n**你可以**：先去 [Canva](https://canva.com) 用中文搜\"Logo\"，模板里改，非常简单。\n\n---\n\n**或者**：你告诉我更具体的要求（如想要什么颜色、什么风格），我帮你用文字描述，你可以拿着描述去找设计师或AI生成。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":14914,"output":452,"cacheRead":17412,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32778,"cost":{"input":0.0044742,"output":0.0005424,"cacheRead":0.0005223599999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005538960000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773498616134}}
