{"type":"message","id":"173b6c0d","parentId":"a2aa9252","timestamp":"2026-03-14T14:31:58.188Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The browser stopped. Let me give Roger a direct prompt he can use on any AI image generation platform, and also suggest an easier way.","thinkingSignature":"7b72c7a059651e9ffca6a88af36dfceb11515f8bf728117908a11e5701630a82"},{"type":"text","text":"由于当前环境图片生成工具有依赖问题，我给你一个**直接可用的Prompt**，你去任意AI生图平台粘贴即可：\n\n---\n\n## 🎨 MNEX Logo Prompt（直接复制）\n\n```\nMNEX technology IP auction trading platform logo, letter M formed by abstract network nodes and connection lines, blue to purple gradient, patent document or chip icon integrated, modern minimalist style, white background, professional business aesthetic, vector style, clean sleek design\n```\n\n**中文描述**：\n```\nMNEX技术IP竞拍交易平台logo，字母M由抽象网络节点和连接线组成，蓝紫渐变，融合专利文件或芯片图标，现代简约风格，白色背景，专业商业感，矢量风格\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 推荐平台（免费使用）\n\n| 平台 | 网址 | 免费额度 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| **Leonardo.ai** | leonardo.ai | 每天150点 |\n| **Canva AI** | canva.com | 免费版够用 |\n| **标智客** | biaomake.com | 免费 |\n\n**操作步骤**：\n1. 打开 Leonardo.ai\n2. 注册/登录\n3. 粘贴上面的Prompt\n4. 生成后下载\n\n---\n\n**或者告诉我**：你更喜欢什么颜色？我重新调整Prompt 😊"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":26261,"output":293,"cacheRead":17412,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43966,"cost":{"input":0.0078783,"output":0.0003516,"cacheRead":0.0005223599999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00875226}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773498710095}}
